                  <decoDesc>
                    <summary>
                    Miniatures (added in the late twentieth-century by “the speckled garment ‎artist”)‎
                  </summary>
                    <decoNote type = "frame" xml:id="d01">Decorative designs: <locus target = "#1r #94r #137r"/>(<foreign xml:lang = "gez">ሐረግ፡</foreign> using black and red); <locus target = "#8v #17r #26r #38r #47r #54r #64v #77v #87v #93v #108r #120r #123r #123v #129v #136v #150r #155v #156v"/> (dotted line using alternating black and red);  <locus target = "#136r, #164r #164v"/> (black and red lines connecting stops).</decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d02"><locus target="#5r"></locus><desc> The Archangel <persName ref = "PRS7049Michael"/> <ref type = "authFile" corresp ="AT1082Angel"/>, copied erasing the text of Ps 7:10–18</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d03"><locus target="#20r"></locus><desc>The Madonna and Child, <ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1031VirginAndChild">, copied erasing the text of Ps 23:9–24:7</ref></desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d04"><locus target="#37r"></locus><desc>Saint George and the Dragon, <ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1069GeorgeandDragon">, copied erasing the text of Ps 39:11–40:2</ref></desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d05"><locus target="#58r"></locus><desc>The Annunciation, <ref type ="authFile" corresp="AT1002Annunciation"/>, copied erasing the text of Ps 65:18–66:6</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d06"><locus target="#76r"></locus><desc>A miniature of <ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1025NativityJesus"></ref>, copied erasing the text of Ps 79:2–11</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d08"><locus target="#117r"></locus><desc>Mary Enthroned, <ref type ="authFile" corresp="AT1062CoronationMary"/>, copied erasing the text of Ps 118:99–110</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d07"><locus target="#95r"></locus><desc>The Flight to Egypt <ref type = "authFile" corresp = "AT1016Flight"/>, copied erasing the text of Ps 101:22–102:1</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d09"><locus target="#136r"></locus><desc>Moses with the Tablets of the Law <ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1024MosesLaw">, with caption <foreign xml:lang = "gez">ቅዱስ፡ ነቢይ፡ ሙሴ፡ ምስለ፡ ፅለቱ፡ ወምስለ፡ ደቀ፡፡መዛሙሩቱ።</foreign></ref>, copied erasing the text of Ps 150:1–151:4</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d010"><locus target="#151r"></locus><desc>The Presentation of Jesus at the Temple <ref type = "authFile" corresp ="AT1027PresentationJesus"/></desc></decoNote>
